DSS.title: Add Select All for Countries on Resource Edit

comments.body:
Received another request for this feature. Would like a means to apply the tags for "all countries" to a given resource. Right now we have a standard autocomplete widget in the record edit form.![Screen Shot 2023-01-05 at 8.44.00 AM.png](https://images.zenhubusercontent.com/5cba088397df763a9090ce23/fe7e803e-dbc9-4ad5-92e2-b08109c934a5)![Screen Shot 2023-01-05 at 8.44.00 AM.png](https://images.zenhubusercontent.com/5cba088397df763a9090ce23/799920ec-aa21-4aba-b204-e505dc9d55a8)

Perhaps we could workout a toggle option on the "New" record form. Where the user choses between applying all countries or seeing the standard form element to apply a small number of country options.
